
Create submodule
git submodule add https://github.com/esmf-org/esmf
git submodule add https://github.com/Unidata/netcdf-c

   cat .gitmodules
   check git status
   git diff
   git diff --cached --submodule

Commit:
git commit -am 'Adding esmf module'

Publish:
git push origin master

Checking a project with submodules:
git clone
git submodule init
git submodule update
